Bonus list:

- Best-fit optimized allocation algorithm
- Headers for allocated chunks
- Implementation of calloc
- Implementation of reallocf
- Hex dump with show_alloc_mem_ex()
- The program is thread safe thanks to the g_mutex lock and unlock
- Logging of allocation history (mallocs, frees, reallocs)
- Ability to set DMALLOC_LOGS environment to print loggings on standart input
- Defragmentation of memory when TINY or SMALL is fully freed (kinda half defrag)
